<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>KITSU_LIVE – Impressum</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --primary-dark: #0f0f1e;
      --secondary-dark: #1a1a2e;
      --tertiary-dark: #2d2d44;
      --neon-cyan: #00d4ff;
      --neon-magenta: #ff006e;
      --neon-purple: #b537f2;
      --text-light: #e0e0ff;
      --text-dim: #a0a0c0;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--secondary-dark) 100%);
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    /* Back link */
    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: var(--neon-cyan);
    }

    .back-arrow {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* Card */
    .card {
      background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.85);
      border: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 36px 32px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2),
        0 0 50px rgba(181, 55, 242, 0.08),
        inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04);
    }

    /* Header */
    .card-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .station-label {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--neon-cyan);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-light);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    /* Sections */
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .section:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--neon-cyan);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .section-body {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .section-body a {
      color: var(--neon-magenta);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease, text-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .section-body a:hover {
      color: var(--neon-cyan);
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
    }

    /* Disclaimer box */
    .notice-box {
      background: rgba(181, 55, 242, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(181, 55, 242, 0.25);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .notice-box strong {
      color: var(--neon-purple);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .card-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
      font-size: 10px;
      color: rgba(160, 160, 192, 0.5);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <a href="index.html" class="back-link">
      <span class="back-arrow">←</span> Zurück zum Radio
    </a>

    <div class="card">

      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="station-label">KITSU_LIVE</div>
        <h1 class="page-title">Impressum</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG</div>
        <div class="section-body">
          Max Mustermann<br>
          Musterstraße 12<br>
          12345 Musterstadt<br>
          Deutschland
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Kontakt</div>
        <div class="section-body">
          E-Mail: <a href="mailto:kontakt@beispiel.de">kontakt@beispiel.de</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Verantwortlich für den Inhalt</div>
        <div class="section-body">
          Max Mustermann<br>
          (Anschrift wie oben)
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Haftungsausschluss</div>
        <div class="section-body">
          Die Inhalte dieser Seite wurden mit größter Sorgfalt erstellt. Für die Richtigkeit, Vollständigkeit und Aktualität der Inhalte kann jedoch keine Gewähr übernommen werden.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="notice-box">
        <strong>Hinweis:</strong> Bitte ersetze die Platzhalterdaten (Name, Adresse, E-Mail) durch deine echten Angaben. Ein Impressum ist in Deutschland gesetzlich vorgeschrieben.
      </div>

      <div class="card-footer">
        © 2025 KITSU_LIVE · Alle Rechte vorbehalten
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
